**  TB1.TB2
0CANCEL
1CHANGE
2ADD
**  ER
E-01 UPDATE INSTRUCTION IS <0.1.2>
E-02 INPUT PGM
E-03 PGM IS WRONG
E-04 ADD WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F EXIST
E-05 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F NOT EXIST
E-06 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F IS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-07 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F NOT EXIST
E-08 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F IS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-09 INPUT SYSTEM (LAARGE)
E-10 SYSTEM (LAARGE) IS 1-14
E-11 INPUT OUTPUT METHOD (MEDIUM)
E-12 OUTPUT METHOD (MEDIUM) IS 1-7
E-13 OUTPUT METHOD (SMALL) IS BLANK, 1-3
E-14 INPUT CONTROL DEPARTMENT
E-15 CONTROL DEPARTMENT IS 1-20
